lead_paragraph: Nolan Arenado, who led the majors with 130 RBIs last season, doubled in a run in his first at-bat of the spring in the Colorado Rockies' 6-3 loss to the Arizona Diamondbacks on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Arenado Starts Fast in Rockies' 6-3 Opening Loss to D-Backs
